com.opengamma.strata.basics

Interface CalculationTarget

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    FinanceTrade, ProductTrade, ResolvableTrade<T>, SecuritizedProductTrade, Trade
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BondFutureOptionTrade, BondFutureTrade, BulletPaymentTrade, CapitalIndexedBondTrade, CdsTrade, CmsTrade, DeliverableSwapFutureTrade, EquityTrade, FixedCouponBondTrade, FraTrade, FxNdfTrade, FxSingleTrade, FxSwapTrade, FxVanillaOptionTrade, GenericSecurityTrade, IborCapFloorTrade, IborFixingDepositTrade, IborFutureOptionTrade, IborFutureTrade, SecurityTrade, SwaptionTrade, SwapTrade, TermDepositTrade

    public interface CalculationTarget
    The target of calculation within a system.

    All financial instruments that can be the target of calculations implement this market interface. For example, a trade or position.

    All implementations of this interface must be immutable and thread-safe.
